comments: Turner (IND) briefly engages with Birch (TOR), which doesn't affect his ability to set the pick.
VanVleet (TOR) loses control of the ball on his own.
McConnell (IND) makes marginal contact with Birch (TOR), which doesn't affect his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
VanVleet (TOR) briefly engages with Holiday (IND) off-ball and separates.
Sabonis (IND) is firming up when marginal contact occurs to Trent Jr.'s (TOR) side on the screen.
Trent Jr. (TOR) dislodges the ball before marginal contact occurs with Duarte (IND).
Anunoby (TOR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
VanVleet (TOR) brushes Holiday's (IND) body during the driving shot attempt, and the contact is marginal.
McConnell (IND) places two hands on VanVleet's (TOR) front in the backcourt and affects his SQBR.
Duarte (IND) is retreating his arms into a vertical position when marginal contact occurs with Barnes (TOR) on the layup attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Duarte's (IND) driving shot attempt as he cleanly blocks the shot before incidental contact occurs.
Anunoby (TOR) jumps from point A to point B when he makes lower-body contact with Duarte (IND) after his release on the shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in McConnell's (IND) path during the pick in the backcourt.
Sabonis (IND) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR) on the perimeter.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes himself in the backcourt when he receives the pass.
Sabonis (IND) dislodges the incoming pass as he simultaneously makes marginal contact with Birch (TOR).
Duarte (IND) makes contact with VanVleet's (TOR) arm and head on the perimeter.
VanVleet (TOR) makes marginal contact with Holiday (IND), which doesn't affect his ability to pass.
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Barnes (TOR).
Birch (TOR) extends two hands into Holiday's (IND) side, which affects his SQBR.
Turner (IND) is in a wide screening position when he continues to deliver contact into Birch (TOR) on the screen.
Birch (TOR) legally contests Sabonis' (IND) jump shot attempt.
